data.revised_prompt: A detailed 4k digital art showing a futuristic scene in a dark virtual void. The main focus is a holographic artificial intelligence core interface that is suspended. The interface is illuminated with glowing cyan and gold energy rings that wrap around, showcasing a minimalist tech aesthetic. Visible are intricate data streams pulsating through the rings, providing a look of interconnectivity and information flow. The entire scene is accentuated with cinematic lighting that enhances the depth and provides a sense of advanced technology.
